query:
SET @sjc_id = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name LIKE '%San Joaquin%' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1);

-- Pediatric protocols
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, protocolEffectiveDate, protocolYear, createdAt)
VALUES 
(@sjc_id, 'PCAR-01', 'Pediatric Cardiac Arrest', 'Pediatric Cardiac', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Cardiac Arrest. Age-appropriate CPR, defibrillation, and medication dosing.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'PCAR-02', 'Pediatric Bradycardia', 'Pediatric Cardiac', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Bradycardia. Assessment, oxygenation, and medication therapy.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'PCAR-03', 'Pediatric Tachycardia', 'Pediatric Cardiac', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Tachycardia. SVT management, vagal maneuvers, and adenosine.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'PRES-01', 'Pediatric Asthma', 'Pediatric Respiratory', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Asthma. Bronchodilator therapy and corticosteroids with weight-based dosing.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'PRES-02', 'Pediatric Respiratory Distress', 'Pediatric Respiratory', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Respiratory Distress. Assessment, positioning, and oxygen therapy.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'PRES-03', 'Croup/Epiglottitis', 'Pediatric Respiratory', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Croup and Epiglottitis. Nebulized epinephrine, dexamethasone, and airway management.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'PNRO-01', 'Pediatric Seizures', 'Pediatric Neurological', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Seizures. Benzodiazepine administration with weight-based dosing.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'PNRO-02', 'Pediatric Hypoglycemia', 'Pediatric Neurological', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Hypoglycemia. Dextrose administration with age-appropriate concentrations.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'PENV-01', 'Pediatric Anaphylaxis', 'Pediatric Environmental', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Anaphylaxis. Weight-based epinephrine dosing and supportive care.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'PTRA-01', 'Pediatric Trauma', 'Pediatric Trauma', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Trauma. Age-appropriate assessment and treatment considerations.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'PODP-01', 'Pediatric Overdose', 'Pediatric Overdose', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Overdose. Weight-based antidote dosing and supportive care.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'PGEN-01', 'Pediatric Pain Management', 'Pediatric General', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Pain Management. Weight-based analgesic dosing.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),

-- Neonatal protocols
(@sjc_id, 'NRES-01', 'Neonatal Resuscitation', 'Neonatal', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Neonatal Resuscitation. NRP guidelines, warming, stimulation, and ventilation.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW()),
(@sjc_id, 'NCAR-01', 'Neonatal Cardiac Arrest', 'Neonatal', 'San Joaquin County ALS Treatment Protocol for Neonatal Cardiac Arrest. Chest compressions, epinephrine, and volume resuscitation.', 'https://www.sjgov.org/department/ems/policies', '2025-08-22', 2025, NOW());
